! CodeMirror 6 Editor

A modern text editor for TiddlyWiki based on [[CodeMirror 6|https://codemirror.net/]].

!! Features

* ''Syntax Highlighting'' - Full TiddlyWiki wikitext highlighting with support for nested languages
* ''Autocompletion'' - Smart completions for tiddler titles, macros, widgets, filters, and more
* ''Code Folding'' - Collapse widgets, pragmas, code blocks, and other structures
* ''Multiple Cursors'' - Edit multiple locations simultaneously
* ''Search & Replace'' - Powerful search with regex support
* ''Undo/Redo'' - Full history with unlimited undo levels
* ''Keyboard Shortcuts'' - Extensive keyboard support for efficient editing

!! Keyboard Shortcuts

|!Shortcut |!Action |
|`Ctrl+Z` |Undo |
|`Ctrl+Shift+Z` / `Ctrl+Y` |Redo |
|`Ctrl+F` |Find |
|`Ctrl+H` |Find and Replace |
|`Ctrl+G` |Go to next match |
|`Ctrl+Shift+G` |Go to previous match |
|`Ctrl+D` |Select next occurrence |
|`Ctrl+/` |Toggle line comment |
|`Tab` |Indent / Accept completion |
|`Shift+Tab` |Outdent |
|`Ctrl+Space` |Trigger autocompletion |
|`Alt+Up` |Move line up |
|`Alt+Down` |Move line down |
|`Ctrl+Shift+K` |Delete line |

!! Configuration

Configure the editor via ''Control Panel > Settings > CodeMirror'':

* Theme selection
* Font size and font family
* Tab size and indentation
* Line wrapping
* Bracket matching
* Auto-close brackets
* And many more options

!! Optional Plugins

Extend the editor with additional plugins:

* ''Lint'' - Highlight potential issues in your content
* ''Vim/Emacs Keymaps'' - Alternative keyboard bindings
* ''Snippets'' - Custom code snippets with tab stops
* ''Language Packs'' - Syntax highlighting for JavaScript, CSS, JSON, etc.
* ''Themes'' - Additional color themes
